                    <li><strong>Coburg Lake and Surrounds:</strong> Focusing on revegetation.</li>
                    <li><strong>East Coburg:</strong> Maintaining indigenous gardens.</li>
                    <li><strong>Edgars Creek:</strong> Working along the tributary.</li>
                    <li><strong>Malcolm Creek and Grasslands:</strong> Protecting native grasslands.</li>
                    <li><strong>Merri Mumong (MECCARG):</strong> Cultural burning and land care.</li>
